OL,3,CFormer Lord Mayor resigns from Labour
OL,4,Cover party's Israel-Gaza stance
OL,6,FThe first ethnic minority Lord Mayor
OL,7,Fof Newcastle has resigned from the
OL,8,FLabour party.
OL,10,FHabib Rahman strongly criticised the
OL,11,Fparty over the party's approach to
OL,12,FIslamophobia and the Israel-Gaza
OL,13,Fconflict.
OL,15,FCouncillor Rahman, who moved to the UK
OL,16,Ffrom Bangladesh, took on Newcastle's
OL,17,Fceremonial Lord Mayor role for a year
OL,18,Ffrom May 2021.
