OL,3,CFormer Lord Mayor resigns from Labour
OL,4,Cover party's Israel-Gaza stance
OL,6,FIn a letter to the Labour leader Sir
OL,7,FKeir Starmer on Friday 26 January, he
OL,8,Fwrote: "During my 13 years as a Labour
OL,9,Fcouncillor, I have faced various forms
OL,10,Fof abuse within the party."
OL,12,FHe said: "I have... concluded that the
OL,13,Fparty does not take other forms of
OL,14,Fracism including Islamophobia and hate
OL,15,Fcrimes as seriously as it does
OL,16,Fantisemitism."
