OL,3,CFormer Lord Mayor resigns from Labour
OL,4,Cover party's Israel-Gaza stance
OL,6,FHis letter also includes: "I cannot
OL,7,Faccept your inhumane position in
OL,8,Fsupport of the Israeli government's
OL,9,Fcontinuous bombardment of innocent
OL,10,FPalestinian people."
OL,12,F"Your reluctance to call for an
OL,13,Fimmediate ceasefire indicates that you
OL,14,Fno longer have the moral authority to
OL,15,Fbe the leader of the Labour party."
OL,17,FA spokesperson for Newcastle Labour
OL,18,FGroup said: "As a Labour group we are
OL,19,Fincredibly sad to hear of Councillor
OL,20,FHabib Rahman's decision today.
