OL,3,CFormer Lord Mayor resigns from Labour
OL,4,Cover party's Israel-Gaza stance
OL,6,F"We would like to thank him for all he
OL,7,Fhas done for his constituents in
OL,8,FElswick and the City of Newcastle at
OL,9,Flarge."
OL,11,F"The Labour Party is an anti-racist
OL,12,Fparty, committed to combating and
OL,13,Fcampaigning against all forms of
OL,14,Fracism, including antisemitism and
OL,15,FIslamophobia."
OL,17,FCllr Rahman, whose father was murdered
OL,18,Fin a racist attack in Wallsend in
OL,19,F1977, said he was a dedicated
OL,20,Fcampaigner for equality and against
OL,21,Fhate crime.
